TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select a.as_of_date, a.inventory_type, d.facility_code,b.Garm_per_Pkg_Qty, a.parent_item_id as parent_id,b.style_num, a.item_id as child_id, b.sku, b.brand_name, b.gender_desc, b.gender_category_desc, b.level_3_name, a.garments, a.dollars, a.uom, case when c.lifecycle_code = 'N' then '6' when c.lifecycle_code = 'O' then '4' else '1' end as lifecycle_code, 'comp' shipper_comp, d.facility_name, s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE put_up_cd from inventory_exploded a join( select i.item_id item_id, i.Garm_per_Pkg_Qty Garm_per_Pkg_Qty, i.style_num style_num,i.sku sku, e.brand_name brand_name, e.gender_desc gender_desc, e.gender_category_desc gender_category_desc, e.level_3_name level_3_name from item i, style_master_1 e where i.style_num = e.style_num and i.division_group = e.division_group)b on a.item_id = b.item_id join item bb on bb.item_id=a.parent_item_id join sku_lifecycle_class c on a.item_id = c.item_id join slba_facility d on a.facility_id = d.facility_id left join sap_item s on a.item_id = s.slba_item_id where a.as_of_date between c.start_date and c.end_date and a.as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 AS EXPR1 FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE))) and a.parent_item_id in (select distinct item_id from bi_inventory where legacy_lob = 'Socks' and as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 AS EXPR1 FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE))))

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select a.as_of_date as_of_date, a.inventory_type inventory_type, d.facility_code facility_code,b.Garm_per_Pkg_Qty Garm_per_Pkg_Qty, a.item_id as parent_id, b.style_num style_num, 0 as child_id, b.sku sku, b.brand_name brand_name, b.gender_desc gender_desc, b.gender_category_desc gender_category_desc, b.level_3_name level_3_name, a.garments garments, a.dollars dollars, a.uom uom, c.mapped_class_code as lifecycle_code, 'shipper' shipper_comp,d.facility_name facility_name, s.LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE as put_up_cd from bi_inventory a join(SELECT ITEM.ITEM_ID ITEM_ID,ITEM.Garm_per_Pkg_Qty Garm_per_Pkg_Qty,ITEM.style_num STYLE_NUM, item.sku sku,E.brand_name brand_name, e.gender_desc gender_desc, e.gender_category_desc gender_category_desc, e.level_3_name level_3_name, ITEM.sap_material_num, ITEM.sap_grid_value FROM item ITEM ,style_master_1 e where item.style_num = e.style_num and item.division_group = e.division_group )b on a.item_id = b.item_id left join sap_item s on b.sap_material_num = s.material_num AND b.sap_grid_value = s.grid_value join sku_lifecycle_class_l c on a.item_id = c.item_id join slba_facility d on a.facility_id = d.facility_id where a.legacy_lob = 'Socks' and a.as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 AS EXPR1 FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE))) and a.as_of_date between c.start_date and c.end_date and a.item_id in (select distinct parent_item_id from inventory_exploded where as_of_date = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 AS EXPR1 FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE))) )
